Enum Source

    • java.lang.Enum<Source>

    public enum Source
extends java.lang.Enum<Source>
implements sailpoint.tools.Localizable
    Constant definitions for "sources", used in several places in the model to record the origin of something.

      • fromString

        public static Source fromString(java.lang.String str)
        Utility to derive the Source value from a string. This converter is relaxed about case sensitivity so older RoleAssignment sources that normally used all lower case can be auto-upgraded.

        This will return null and not throw if the string is not the name of one of the built-in sources. This indicates that this is a custom source.
